## Documentation Organization
- All docs in `docs/` subfolders use date-based organization: `docs/<subfolder>/YYYY-MM-DD/`
- Use ISO date format: `2025-08-25`
- File names: concise, no dates (date in folder path)
- Save detailed plans to `docs/plans/YYYY-MM-DD/`
- Save research and brainstorming discussions to `docs/brainstorm/YYYY-MM-DD/`
- Add docs cleanup task when session ends

## Document purposes
- Plan files go into `docs/plans/...``
- Guide files go into `docs/guides/...``
- Issues and Bugs invesgitations go into `docs/investigations/...``
- Progresses, updates go into `docs/notes/...``
- Tasks for features or updates go into `tasks/...``
- Bugs go into `bugs/...``

## Templates
- When creating new task, copy precisely from `tasks/task.template.md` then make edits
- When creating new bug, copy precisely from `bugs/bug.template.md` then make edits
